headline: Trade Tracker: Amy Raskin shares her latest portfolio moves
summary: Amy Raskin, chief investment officer at Chevy Chase Trust, joins CNBC's 'Halftime Report' to explain why she bought Ascendis Pharma and is buying more Cognex, SLB, Fanuc, AIA, CrowdStrike and Impinj.
